                in fst x' (d k)
                  ‚Č°‚ü® elem-prop n‚āÄ m‚āÄ x' ‚ü©
                őĪ-pred n‚āÄ m‚āÄ x'
                  ‚Č°‚ü® cong (őĽ z ‚Üí fst (wit n‚āÄ z) m‚āÄ) (transportTransport‚ĀĽ SpB‚Č°S s) ‚ü©
                fst (wit n‚āÄ s) m‚āÄ
                  ‚Č°‚ü® all-false m‚āÄ ‚ü©
                false ‚ąé

              contra : true ‚Č° false
              contra =
                true
                  ‚Č°‚ü® sym (IsCommRingHom.pres1 (snd x')) ‚ü©
                fst x' ūĚüôB
                  ‚Č°‚ü® cong (fst x') (sym fJ-eq) ‚ü©
