      A'-closed : (s : fst S) ‚Üí isClosedProp (A' s)
      A'-closed s = A-closed (q s)

      B'-closed : (s : fst S) ‚Üí isClosedProp (B' s)
      B'-closed s = B-closed (q s)

      A'B'-disjoint : ClosedSubsetsDisjoint S (A' , A'-closed) (B' , B'-closed)
      A'B'-disjoint s a'x b'x = AB-disjoint (q s) (a'x , b'x)

      separated : ‚ą• ő£[ D ‚ąą DecSubsetOfStone S ] (ClosedSubDec S (A' , A'-closed) D) √ó (ClosedSubNotDec S (B' , B'-closed) D) ‚ą•‚āĀ
